data.description: Great starter home or investment property. Invest in your future. Stop paying rent. This ranch on 2 parcels could be your new home or a great investment property. Large living room with nice laminate flooring. Spacious open kitchen/dining area. 2 nice size bedrooms and a full bath on the main floor. Full unfinished basement is a blank slate. Finish part or all or use as work/play space. Newer High Efficiency (Rheem 96) gas furnace, new water heater and metal roof in 2023. One car garage and nice back yard PLUS that extra lot makes a huge yard or you could build a rental house or huge garage or tennis court if you prefer. It's hard to find a home for under $200K these days and this could be yours.
